      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "The user has declined to provide their insurance or confirm self-pay.\n\nAcknowledge their concern warmly, then explain: \"I completely \nunderstand, and I don't want to push you on anything you're \nnot comfortable with. The thing is, the clinic does need all \nof these details to get your appointment set up properly.\"\n\nThen offer three options:\n1. Transfer: \"If you'd prefer, I can connect you with someone \n   at the front desk who can help directly.\"\n2. End: \"Otherwise, you're always welcome to call us back when you're ready — we'll be here!\"\n\nWait for the user to choose."
      }
    },
